hadiths[142]{hadithnumber,text}:
5379,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamein khitab farmaney ke liye eik jagah khadey huey to aapney us waqt se lekar qiyame-qiyamat tak honey waley tamam waqiyat bayan farmaai , yad rakhney walon ne usey yad rakha , aur bhulne waley ne usey bhula diya, aur merey ye sathi us se khub aagah hain, aur un (mazkura chizon) mein se jab wo chiz roonumaa hoti (samne aati) hai jisey mein bhool chuka tha to usey dekh kar meri yad taza ho jati hai, jis tarah aadmi kisi ghayeb ho janey waley aadmi ke chehrey ko yad karta hai, phir jab wo usey dekhta hai to wo usey pehchan leta hai. muttafaq aleh."
5380,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''dilon par fitney is tarah musalsal pesh kiye jaeyngey jis tarah chatai ke tinkey musalsal hotey hain, jis mein wo pewast kar diya gaya, is par eik siyah nukta laga diya jata hai, aur jis dil ne usey qubul karney se inkar kiya, is par eik safed nukta laga diya jata hai yahan tak ke dil do qism ke ho jaeyngey, un mein se eik dil safed pathar ki tarah chamak daar ho jaeyga jisey qiyame-qiyamat tak koi fitna nuqsan nahin pahuncha sakta, jabkey doosra dil siyah raakh ki manind hoga jaisey ulta bartan ho, wo na to neki ko pehchanta hai aur na burai ko , wo sirf wohi janta hai jo uski khaahishat se is mein pewast kar diya jaey.'' rawahu Muslim."
5381,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein do hadisein bayan kin , maine un mein se eik to dekh li jabkey dusri ka intizar hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein hadees bayan ki ke amanat (emaan daari) aadmiyon ke dilon ki jad (fitrat) mein utri , phir unhoney Quran se seekha , phir sunnat se .'' phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne is (emaan) ke uth janey ke mutalliq hamein hadees bayan ki, farmaya : ''aadmi ghafil hoga to eman uskey dil se utha liya jaeyga, uska nishan nuqtey ki tarah reh jaeyga, phir wo dobara ghafil hoga to is (emaan) ko utha liya jaeyga to aabley ki tarah is par nishan reh jaeyga jaisey to ne apney paaon par angaara ludhkaayaa ho, wo aabla bin jaey aur to usey phula hua dekhey halanke is mein koi chiz nahin, aur log subah karengey aur koi eik bhi amanat ada nahin karega, kaha jaeyga ke falan qabiley main eik amanat daar shakhs hai, aur kisi aur aadmi ke mutalliq kaha jaeyga ke wo kis qadr aqlmand hai, uska kitna zarf hai aur wo kis qadr bardasht wala hai, halanke uskey dil mein raai ke daney ke barabar bhi eman nahin hoga.'' muttafaq aleh."
5382,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se khair ke mutalliq puchha kartey they jabkey main aap se shar ke mutalliq , us andeshe ke peshe-nazar puchha karta tha ke wo kahin mujhey apni giraft mein na le-ley , wo bayan kartey hain, maine arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! ham jahiliyat aur shar mein mubtala they, Allah ne hamein is khair se nawaz diya, to kya is khair ke baad koi shar bhi aaeyga? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haan.'' maine arz kiya us shar ke baad koi khair bhi aaeygi? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haan ! lekin is mein kamzori hogi.'' maine arz kiya, uski kamzori kya hogi? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kuchh log meri sunnat aur merey tareeqe ke khilaf chalengey, unki baaz baaton ko tum achchhaa samjhogey aur baaz ko bura.'' maine arz kiya : kya us khair ke baad shar hoga? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haan,  jahannam ke darwazon par dawat deney waley hongey, jisney unki dawat ko qubul kar liya to wo usko is mein phenk dengey.'' maine arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! unka Taaruf : kara den, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo hamarey hi qabiley se hongey aur wo hamari zaban mein kalam karengey.'' maine arz kiya, agar us (zamaney) ne mujhey pa liya to aap mujhey kya hukm farmatey hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''musalmanon ki jamaat aur unke ameer ke sath lag jana.'' maine arz kya, agar unki jamaat na ho aur na unka Imam (to phir kya karun?) aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''un tamam firqon se alag ho jana chahey (chaahen) tumhen darkht ki jadein chabani paden yahan tak ke tumhen usi haalat mein maut aa jaey.'' aur Sahih Muslim ki riwayat mein hai, farmaya : ''merey baad hukmran hongey jo na to meri hidayat aur tareeqe se raahnumai lengey aur na meri sunnat ke mutabiq amal karengey aur un mein kuchh log aisey hongey, jinkey dhaanchey insani aur dil shetan hongey.'' Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! agar main ye soorate-haal dekhun to main kya karun? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ameer ki baat sun'na aur uski itaat karna, agar-che tujhey maara jaey aur tumhara maal ley liya jaey, tum suno aur itaat karo.'' muttafaq aleh."
5383,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aisey fitnon ke aaney se pehley , nek aamaal karney mein jaldi kar lo, jo taareek raat ke tukdon ki tarah hongey, aadmi subah ke waqt momin hoga to Sham ke waqt kafir jabkey Sham ke waqt momin hoga to subah ke waqt kafir wo duniya ke maal aur daulat ke iwaz apna Deen bech dega.'' rawahu Muslim."
5384,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''an-qareeb aisey fitney paida hongey ke un mein bethney wala khadey honey waley se behtar hoga, khada honey wala chalney waley se behtar hoga aur chalney wala daudney waley se behtar hoga. jisney unki taraf jhank kar dekha to wo usey bhi apni lapet mein ley lengey , jo shakhs koi panahga ya bachaaw ki jagah paey to wo wahan panah hasil kar ley.'' aur Muslim ki riwayat mein hai, farmaya : ''fitney paida hongey, un mein soney wala jaagney waley se behtar hoga jabkey un mein jaagney wala khadey honey waley se behtar hoga aur khada honey wala un mein daudney waley se behtar hoga, jo shakhs koi panah-gaah ya bachaaw ki jagah paey to wo wahan panah hasil kar ley.'' muttafaq aleh."
5385,"Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''an-qareeb fitney barpa hongey, sun lo ! phir badey fitney hongey, sun lo ! phir aisey azeem fitney hongey ke un mein bethney wala, chalney waley se behtar hoga, un mein chalney wala daudney waley se behtar hoga, sun lo ! jab ye waqey ho jaeyn to jiskey paas oont hon to wo apney oonton ke sath mashghool ho jaey, jiski bakriyan hon wo apni bakriyon ke sath mashghool ho jaey aur jiski zamin ho to wo apni zamin ke sath mashghool ho jaey.'' eik aadmi ne arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! bataeyn ke jis shakhs ke paas oont hon na bakriyan aur na hi zamin (to wo kya karey?), farmaya : ''wo apni talwaar ka qasd (irada) karey aur usey pathar par maar kar kund kar dey (us ki tezi khatam kar dey), phir agar istataat ho (wahan se) bhag nikley (ke fitney usey apni lapet mein na ley lein) ta ke wo bach sakey , aey Allah ! kya maine (pegham Ilaahi) pahuncha diya?'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne teen baar farmaya , to eik aadmi ne arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey bataeyn agar mujhey majbur kar diya jaey yahan tak ke mujhey do safon (jamaaton, girohon) mein se kisi eik ke sath ley jaya jaey to koi apni talwaar se mujhey maarey ya koi teer aaye aur wo mujhey qatl kar dey (to qatil aur maqtool ke barey mein kya hukm hai?) aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo (qatil) apney aur tumharey gunah ka (bojh) lekar wapis aaeyga aur wo jahannami hoga.'' rawahu Muslim."
5386,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qarib hai ke musalman ka behtareen maal bakriyan hon, wo fitnon se apney Deen ki hifazat ke liye un bakriyon ko lekar pahadon ki chotiyon aur barish barasney ki jagahon par bhag jaey.'' Bukhari."
5387,"Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Madiney ke kisi buland makaan par chadhey to farmaya : ''kya tum dekh rahey ho jo main dekh raha hun?'' unhoney arz kiya : nahin, farmaya : ''be-shak main fitney dekh raha hun jo tumharey gharon mein barish ke qatron ki tarah dakhil ho rahey hain.'' muttafaq aleh."
5388,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri ummat ki halakat aur tabahi Quraish ke chand nojawan ladkon ke haathon hogi.'' Bukhari."
5389,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''zamana (qiyamat ke) qarib hota jaeyga, ilm khatam kar diya jaeyga, fitney zahir hongey, (dilon mein) bukhl dal diya jaeyga aur harj ziyada ho jaeyga.'' unhoney arz kya, harj kiya hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qatl.'' muttafaq aleh."
5390,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! duniya khatam nahin hogi yahan tak ke logon par eik aisa din bhi aaeyga ke qatil ko malum nahin hoga ke usney kis wajeh se qatl kiya aur maqtool ko malum nahin hoga ke usey kis wajeh se qatl kiya gaya?'' arz kiya gaya, ye kis wajeh se hoga ? farmaya : '' fitney ki wajeh sey, qatil aur maqtool (dono) jahannami hain.'' rawahu Muslim."
5391,"Hazrat Maaqil bin Yasar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''fitney ke (zamaney) mein ibadat karna meri taraf hijrat karney ki tarah hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
5392,"Hazrat Zuber bin Adi bayan kartey hain, ham Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaye to ham ne Hujjaj ki taraf se ham par honey waley zulm ke mutalliq un se shikayat ki to unhoney farmaya : sabr karo, kyonkey tum par jo waqt bhi aa raha hai, uskey baad aaney wala waqt us se bhi ziyada bura hoga yahan tak ke tum apney rab se ja milo.'' maine ye baat tumharey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suni hai. Bukhari."
5393,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Allah ki qism ! main nahin janta ke merey sathi bhool gaey ya unhoney bhul ka izhar kiya, Allah ki qism ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne intihaaye duniya tak honey waley daiyan fitne, jin ki tadaad teen sau se zayed tak pahuncheygi , ke mutalliq bataya , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uska naam , uskey walid ka naam aur uskey qabiley ke naam ke mutalliq hamein bataya. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
5394,"Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey apni ummat ke mutalliq gumrah hukmranon ka andesha hai, jab meri ummat mein talwaar rakh di jaeygi to wo roze-qiyamat tak un se nahin uthai jaeygi.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Tirmizi."
5395,"Hazrat Safina (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''khilaafat tees saal tak hogi, phir badshahat hogi.'' phir Safina bayan kartey hain : Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki khilaafat do saal shumar kar, umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki das saal, Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ki baara saal aur Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ki khilaafat chhe saal shumar kar. rawahu Ahmed, Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
5396,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! kya us khair (yani Islam) ke baad shar hoga jis tarah is se pehley shar (yani kufr) tha? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haan !''maine arz kiya : bachaaw ka koi raasta hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''talwaar.'' maine arz kiya, kya talwaar ke baad (ehale-Islam mein sey) koi baqi hoga? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''amaarat ke nateeje mein fasad hoga, suleh nifaq par hogi aur ittihaad mafad parasti par hoga.'' maine arz kiya, phir kya hoga? farmaya : ''daiyaane-gumrahi zahir hongey, agar Allah ke liye zamin par koi khalifa ho wo (zulm karte hue) teri pusht par maarey aur tera maal le-ley to to uski itaat kar, dusri sura (agar khalifa na ho) to is tarah faut ho ke to darkht ki jad pakdey huey ho.'' maine arz kiya, phir kya hoga? farmaya : ''phir uskey baad dajjaal ka zuhoor hoga uskey sath nehar aur aag hogi , jo shakhs uski aag mein dakhil ho gaya to uska ajr wajib ho gaya aur uskey gunah mita diye gaey, aur jo shakhs uski nehar mein dakhil ho gaya to uska gunah wajib ho gaya aur uska ajr khatam kar diya gaya.'' Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine arz kiya, phir kya hoga? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''phir ghodey ka bachcha paida hoga aur wo abhi sawari ke qabil nahin hoga ke qiyamat qaaim ho jaeygi.'' eik riwayat mein hai, farmaya : ''kadurat par suleh, aur mafad par aitimad hoga.'' maine arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! kadurat par suleh se kya murad hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''logon ke dil (mohabbat ki) us haalat par nahin aaeyngey jis par wo pehley they.'' maine arz kiya, us khair ke baad shar hoga? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''andha behra fitna, us (fitney) par daaiyan hongey (goya) wo jahannam ke darwaze par (khadey) hain, Huzefa ! agar tum darkht ki jad ko pakdey huey faut huey to wo terey liye us se behtar hai ke to un mein se kisi (fitney) ki ittiba karey.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
5397,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main eik roz Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke peechhey gadhey par Sawar tha, jab ham Madina ke gharon se aagey nikal gaey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Abu-Zar ! us waqt tumhari kya kaifiyat hogi jab Madina mein bhook hogi , tum apney bistar se uthogey aur apni Namaz ki jagah tak nahin pahunch sakogey yahan tak ke bhook tumhen mashaqqat mein mubtala kar deygi .'' wo kehtey hain, maine arz kiya : Allah aur uskey Rasool behtar jantey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Abu-Zar ! sawal karney se bachna.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Abu-Zar ! tumhari kya kaifiyat hogi jab Madina mein maut aam hogi yahan tak ke qabr ki jagah ghulam ki qeemat ko pahunch jaeygi?'' wo bayan kartey hain, maine arz kiya, Allah aur uskey Rasool behtar jantey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Abu-Zar ! tum sabr karna.'' farmaya : ''Abu-Zar ! tumhari kya kaifiyat hogi jab Madina mein qatle-aam hoga khoon ahjarizzait (Madina main eik mohalley ya jagah ka naam hai) tak phel jaeyga?'' maine arz kiya, Allah aur uskey Rasool behtar jantey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum unke paas chaley jana jinkey sath tera (deeni ya khooni) talluq hai.'' wo bayan kartey hain, maine arz kiya, main musalleh ho jaaunga. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tab to aap unke sath shareek ho jaaogey.'' maine arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! main kya karun? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar tumhen andesha ho ke talwaar ki tezi tum par ghalib aa jaeygi to phir tum apney kapdey ka kinara apney chehrey par dal lena ta ke wo (qatil) terey aur apney gunah ke sath lotey.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
5398,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tumhari us waqt kya haalat hogi jab tum nikamme logon mein baqi reh jaaogey , unke wadey aur unki amanaten kharab ho jaeyngi aur wo ikhtilaf ka shikar ho jaeyngey, wo is tarah ho jaeyngey.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney eik haath ki ungliyan doosrey haath ki ungliyon mein dalin , unhoney arz kiya, aap mujhey kis chiz ka hukm farmatey hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum jis chiz ko jantey ho usey lazim pakdo aur jisey nahin jantey usey chhod do, aur tum apna khayal rakho aur aam logon (ke amal) ko chhod do.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''apney ghar mein raho , apni zaban par qabu rakho, jo chiz pehchantey ho usey pakdo , jisey nahin pehchantey usey chhod do, tum apni fikr karo aur aam logon ke mamley ko tarak kar do.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney is riwayat ko sahih qarar diya hai. rawahu Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
5399,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qiyamat se pehley andheri raat ke tukdon ki tarah (lagataar) fitney hongey, un mein aadmi subah ke waqt momin hoga to Sham ke waqt kafir aur Sham ke waqt momin hoga to subah ke waqt kafir, un mein bethney wala khadey honey waley se behtar hoga, aur un mein chalney wala daudney waley se behtar hoga, tum un main apni kamaanein tod dalo aur (apni kamanon ke) taant kaat dalo aur apni talwaaron ko pathar par dey maaro, aur agar wo (fitna) tum mein se kisi par dakhil ho gaya to usey chahiye ke wo Adam (Alaihissalam) ke do beton mein se behtar bete ( Haabeel) ki tarah ho jaey.'' aur Abu-Dawood ki unhi se marwi (bayan) hadees mein : ''behtar hai daudney waley sey tak marwi (bayan) hai, phir unhoney arz kiya, aap hamein kya hukm farmatey hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum apney gharon mein jam jana.'' aur Tirmizi ki riwayat mein hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne fitney ke daur ke mutalliq farmaya : ''un main apni kamanon ko tod dena, un mein apney taant kaat dalna aur un fitnon ke waqt apney ghar ki chaar diwaari ko lazim pakadna , aur ibne-Adam (Haabeel) ki tarah ho jana.'' Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees sahih gharib hai. sanad rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Tirmizi."
5400,"Hazrat Umme-Maalik Bahaziya (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne fitney ka zikr kiya to aapney usey qarib qarar diya, maine arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! us (fitney) mein behtareen shakhs kon hoga? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo aadmi jo apney maweshiyon mein hai wo unka bhi haq (yani Zakat) ada karta hai aur apney rab ki ibadat bhi karta hai, aur wo aadmi jo apney ghodey ka sar pakadta hai aur wo apney dushman (kafiron) ko darata hai aur wo usey daratey hain.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5401,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''an-qareeb eik bada fitna hoga jo ke tamam Arbon par muheet hoga, uskey maqtooleen jahannami hain, us barey mein zaban darazi karna talwaar zani karney se bhi ziyada sangeen hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur ibne-Maja."
5402,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''an-qareeb behra , gunga aur andha fitna hoga, jo shakhs uskey qarib jaeyga, to wo usey apni lapet mein le-ley ga, us barey mein zaban darazi karna shamsheer zani (talwar bazi) karney ki tarah hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
5403,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir they ke aapney fitnon ka zikr kiya aur aapney unke mutalliq bahut bayan farmaya yahan tak ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne fitna ihlaas ka zikr farmaya , kisi ne arz kiya, fitna ihlaas kya chiz hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' wo bhagna aur lotna hai, phir fitna khushhali hai uska ubharnaa merey ehale bait ke eik aadmi ke paaon ke nichey se hoga, wo guman kerega ke wo mujh se hai, halanke wo mujh mein se nahin, merey dost to muttaqi log hi hain, phir log eik aisey shakhs (ki imaamat aur hukmrani) par razi ho jaeyngey jaisey peeth eik pasli par ho (yani na-ehal shakhs ko hukmran bana lengey) phir fitna dahimaa is ummat ke her fard par asar andaz hoga, jab kaha jaeyga ke wo khatam ho gaya hai to wo daraz ho jaeyga, us (fitney) mein aadmi subah ke waqt momin hoga to Sham ko kafir yahan tak ke log do girohon mein bat jaeyngey, eman ka giroh jis mein koi nifaq nahin, aur nifaq ka giroh jis mein eman nahin, jab ye surat ho to phir dajjaal ka intizar karo aaj zahir hua ya kal.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
5404,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''arbon ke liye, shar se jo ke qarib aa chuka hai, halakat hai, jisney apna haath rok liya wo kamiyab ho gaya .'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
5405,"Hazrat Miqdad bin Aswad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''sa'adat mand shakhs wo hai jo fitnon se bacha liya gaya, sa'adat mand shakhs wo hai jo fitnon se bacha liya gaya, be-shak sa'adat mand shakhs wo hai jo fitnon se bacha liya gaya, aur jo shakhs un se aazmaya gaya aur usney sabr kiya to uskey liye khushkhabri hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
5406,"Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab meri ummat mein (eik doosrey se ladaai ke liye) talwaar musallat kar di jaeygi to wo roze-qiyamat tak us se nahin uthai jaeygi, aur qiyamat qaaim nahin hogi yahan tak ke meri ummat ke qabaayel mushrekin se ja milengey aur yahan tak ke meri ummat ke qabaayel buton ki puja karengey, aur meri ummat mein tees kazaab hongey aur wo sab daawa karengey ke wo Allah ka Nabi hai, jabkey main khaatimun-nabiyyeen hun merey baad koi Nabi nahin, aur meri ummat ka eik giroh hamesha haq par hoga, wo ghalib rahengey unka mukhalif unka koi nuqsan nahin kar sakega yahan tak ke Allah ka hukm aa jaey.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
5407,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Islam ki chakki paintees ya chhattis ya saintees baras tak (nizam ke tehat) chalti rahegi, agar unhoney (ikhtilaf kiya aur Deen ko be-waqat samajh kar) halakat ko ikhtiyar kiya to phir unki raah wohi hai jo halak huey (jaisey sabiqa ummaten), aur agar unke liye unka Deen qaaim raha to wo unke liye sattar saal tak rahega.'' maine arz kiya : kya (wo sattar baras) us se hain jo baqi reh gaya ya us se hain jo guzar chuka? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us se jo guzar chuka.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
5408,"Hazrat Abu Waaqid Leeshi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab ghazwae-Hunain ke liye rawana huey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mushrekin ke eik darkht ke paas se guzrey , jis par wo apna aslaha latkaayaa kartey they, usey zaat-anwat kaha jata tha, Sahaba ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! hamarey liye bhi zaat-anwat muqarrar farma den jis tarah unke liye zaat-anwat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne (tajjub sey) farmaya : ''Subhanallah ! ye  (baat) to aisey hi hai jaisey Musa (Alaihissalam) ki qom ne kaha tha : ''hamarey liye bhi eik mabud muqarrar kar den jis tarah unke mabud hain.'' us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! tum bhi apney se pehley logon ke tariqon par chalogey.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5409,"Hazrat ibne Musaiyeb (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : ''pehla fitna, yani Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ki shahadat ka waqia, roonumaa hua (saamne aaya) to ghazwae-Badr mein shareek honey wala koi sahabi baqi nahin tha, phir doosra fitna yani waqia Harra (Yazid ke daur mein Madina par hamla hua) to suleh Hudebiya mein shareek koi sahabi baqi nahin tha, phir teesra fitna roonumaa hua to wo khatam na hua jabkey logon mein aql na rahi. Bukhari."
5410,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qiyamat qaaim nahin hogi yahan tak ke do azeem jamaaten qitaal kerengi, unke beech badi qatl w gharat hogi, aur un dono ka daawa eik hi hoga, aur taqriban tees dajjaal, kazaab (jhute) bhejey jaeyngey, wo sab yehi daawa karengey ke wo Allah ke Rasool hain, aur ilm utha liya jaeyga aur zalzaley kasrat se aaeyngey , zamana (qiyamat ka waqt) qarib aa jaeyga, fitney zahir hongey, qatl ziyada hongey, aur tum mein maal ki kasrat ho jaeygi aur rail-pail ho jaeygi, maal wala khayal karega ke uska sadqa kon qubul kerega? aur yahan tak ke wo usey kisi ko deney ki koshish karega to wo shakhs , jisey wo pesh-kash karega , kahega mujhey uski zarurat nahin, aur log badi badi amaaraton ke mutalliq baham (aapas mein) fakhr karengey , eik aadmi doosrey aadmi ki qabr ke paas se guzrey ga to kahega : kaash! ke uski jagah mein hota, aur Suraj maghrib se nikleyga , jab wo (us taraf sey) tulu hoga aur log usey dekh lengey to wo sab eman ley aaeyngey lekin us waqt kisi shakhs ka eman uskey liye faeede-mand nahin hoga jo us se pehley eman daar na ho ya usney apney eman ki haalat mein achhey kaam na kiye hon. aur qiyamat is tarah achcha qaaim hogi ke do aadmiyon ne apney darmiyan apna kapda phela rakha hoga lekin wo na to kharid w farokht kar sakengey aur na usey lapet saken gey. aur eik aadmi apni oontni ka doodh nikal chuka hoga lekin wo usey kha (pi) na saka hoga aur qiyamat qaaim hogi ke eik shakhs apney hoz ki lipaai kar raha hoga lekin wo us se pi nahin sakega , aur qiyamat qaaim hogi ke (eik aadmi) ne apna luqma munh ki taraf utha liya hoga lekin wo usey kha nahin sakega.'' muttafaq aleh."
5411,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qiyamat qaaim nahin hogi yahan tak ke tum eik aisi qom ke sath qitaal karogey jinkey jootey baal waley (yani chamdey) ke hongey, aur yahan tak ke tum turkon se jang karo jin ki aankhen chhoti hongi , chehrey surkh hongey naak chapti hogi aur unke chehrey aisey hongey jaisey teh ba teh dhaal hoti hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
5412,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qiyamat qaaim nahin hogi yahan tak ke tum ajmiyon mein se khuza aur kirmaan walon se qitaal karo, wo surkh chehron waley, chapti naak waley aur chhoti aakhon waley hongey, unke chehrey teh ba teh dhaal jaisey hongey aur unke jootey , baal waley (yani chamdey ke) hongey.'' Bukhari."
5413,Aur sahih Bukhari hi mein Amr bin Taghlab se marwi (bayan) riwayat mein hai : ''chaudey chehron waley.'' Bukhari.
5414,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qiyamat qaaim nahin hogi yahan tak ke musalman , yahudiyon se qitaal karengey, musalman unhen qatl karengey us waqt Yahudi pathar aur darkht ke peechhey chupey ga to wo pathar aur darkht pukar kar kahega : aey musalman ! Allah ke bandey ! ye Yahudi merey peechhey hai, aao aur usey qatl karo, albatta gharqad ka darkht nahin kahega , kyonkey wo yahudiyon ke darakhton mein se hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
5415,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qiyamat qaaim nahin hogi yahan tak ke qahtaan se eik aadmi niklega wo logon ko apni lathi ke sath haankeyga.'' muttafaq aleh."
5416,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''din raat khatam nahin hongey (qiyamat qaaim nahin hogi) yahan tak ke Jah'jaah naami shakhs Maalik bin jaeyga.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''yahan tak ke azad karda ghulamon mein se Jah'jaah naami eik shakhs Maalik bin jaeyga.'' rawahu Muslim."
5417,"Hazrat Jabir bin Samura (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''musalmanon ki eik jamaat aale kisraa ke khazaney par qabza kar legi jo ke safed mehal mein hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
5418,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Kisraa halak ho jaeyga aur uskey baad koi Kisraa nahin hoga, Qaisar halak ho jaeyga aur uskey baad koi Qaisar nahin hoga, aur un dono ke khazaney Allah ki raah mein taqseem kiye jaeyngey.'' aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ladaai ka naam dhoka aur faraib rakha. muttafaq aleh."
5419,"Hazrat Naafe bin Utba (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum jazeera Arab mein jihad karogey to Allah Fateh ata kerega, phir Faaris mein jihad karogey Allah Fateh ata kerega, phir tum Rome par hamla karogey to Allah Fateh ata farmaeyga , phir tum dajjaal se qitaal karogey to Allah Fateh ata farmaeyga.'' rawahu Muslim."
5420,"Hazrat Auf bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main ghazwae-tabuk mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua jabkey aap chamdey ki eik chadar mein they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qiyamat se pehley chhe alamaten shumar karo, meri wafat , phir baitul-Maqdis ki Fateh , phir eik wabaa jo tum mein is tarah phel jaeygi jis tarah bakriyon mein taaoon ki bimari phel jati hai, phir maal ki rai-pel yahan tak ke aadmi ko sau Dinar diye jaeyngey magar wo phir bhi naraz hoga, phir eik aisa fitna barpa hoga jo Arbon ke tamam gharon mein dakhil ho jaeyga, phir tumharey aur roomiyon ke darmiyan suleh hogi , lekin wo ehad shikni (todege) karengey , wo usi parchamon taley tum par hamla karengey aur her parcham taley baara hazar afrad hongey.'' Bukhari."
5421,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qiyamat qaaim nahin hogi yahan tak ke Romi faujein aa'maaq (Madina ke qarib jagah) ya daabq ke maqam par padaaw dalengi, to Madina se us waqt roey zamin ke behtareen afrad par mushtamil eik lashkar unki taraf rawana hoga, jab wo saf bandi kar lengey to Romi kahengey , tum hamarey aur un logon ke darmiyan , jinhon ne hamarey afrad ko qaidi banaya tha, raasta chhod do , ham un se qitaal karna chahtey hain, musalman kahengey , nahin, Allah ki qism ! ham tumharey aur apney bhaiyon ke darmiyan raah khaali nahin chodengey, wo un se qitaal karengey, wo tihai shikast kha jaeyngey, Allah unki kabhi tauba qubul nahin farmaeyga, un mein se tihai qatl kar diye jaeyngey wo Allah ke yahan aa'laa darjey ke shuhda hain, aur tihai Fateh yaab hongey wo kabhi aazamaye nahin jaeyngey wo Qustuntuniya Fateh karengey, wo maale-ghanimat taqseem kar rahey hongey, aur unhoney apni talwaarein zaitun ke darkht ke sath latka di hongi usi doran shetan un mein zor daar aawaz se kahega ke Masih (dajjaal) tumharey ehal w ayaal mein aa chuka hai, wo niklengey aur ye baat batil hogi, jab wo Sham pahunchein gey to wo nikal chuka hoga is beech mein ke wo qitaal ke liye tayyari kar rahey hongey, safein durust kar rahey hongey ke itney mein Namaz ke liye iqaamat kahi jaeygi to Esa bin Maryam (Alaihissalam) nuzool farmaeyngey, aur wo unki imaamat karaeingey, jab Allah ka dushman (dajjaal) unhen dekhega to wo is tarah pighal jaeyga jis tarah namak pani mein ghul jata hai, aur agar wo usey chhod bhi den to wo khud hi gal sadh kar halak ho jaeyga, lekin Allah un (Esa (Alaihissalam)) ke haathon usey qatl karaaeyga, wo apney neze par uska laga hua khoon dikhayengey.'' rawahu Muslim."
5422,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke qiyamat us waqt tak qaaim nahin hogi jab tak meeras taqseem nahin hogi, aur maale-ghanimat (ki taqseem) par khushi mehsus nahin hogi. phir unhoney farmaya : dushman ahale-Sham ke liye jama hongey jabkey ehale-Islam un (roomiyon) ke liye jama ho jaeyngey, musalman eik dastey ko maut ke liye tayyar karengey aur wo ghalba hasil karkey hi wapis aaeyngey , wo qitaal karengey yahan tak ke unke darmiyan raat haael (rukwat) ho jaeygi, aur dono taraf ki faujein ghalba hasil kiye baghair wapis aa jaeyngi , aur muntakhab dastey Shahid kar diye jaeyngey, phir musalman eik dastey ko maut ke liye tayyar karengey aur wo ghalba hasil kiye baghair wapis nahin aaeyngey, wo qitaal kartey rahengey yahan tak ke unke beech raat aadey aa jaeygi, to dono taraf ki faujein ghalba hasil kiye baghair wapis aa jaeyngi aur muntakhab dasta Shahid kar diya jaeyga, phir wo musalman (teesri martaba) eik dasta maut ke liye tayyar karengey wo ghalba hasil karkey wapis aaeyngey, wo qitaal kartey rahengey , yahan tak ke Sham ho jaeygi, aur dono taraf ki faujein ghalba hasil kiye baghair wapis aa jaeyngi aur muntakhab dasta Shahid kar diya jaeyga, jab chotha roz hoga to ehale-Islam ke baqi afrad unke liye uth khadey hongey, to Allah un (kuffar) par hazeemat musallat kar dega , wo khub ladengey us jaisi ladaai kabhi na dekhi gaee hogi yahan tak ke agar parinda unki taraf se guzarnaa chahega to wo murda haalat mein gir padeyga, eik baap ke bete ladaai se pehley giney gaey to wo sau they, lekin ladaai ke baad wo un mein se sirf eik aadmi paeyngey, to kis ghanimat par khushi hogi, aur kon si meeras taqseem ki jaeygi? wo usi beech mein hongey ke wo achcha eik ladaai ke mutalliq sunengey jo ke us se bhi badi hogi, un tak aawaz pahuncheygi, dajjaal unki aulad mein zahir ho chuka hai, unke haathon mein jo kuchh hoga wo usey phenk dengey, aur udhar mutawajjeh hongey, wo khabar hasil karney ke liye das ghud sawaron ko bhejeingey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main unke aur unke baap-daada ke naam aur unke ghodon ke rang pehchanta hun aur wo roey zamin par behtareen ghud sawar hongey.'' rawahu Muslim."
5423,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum ne eik aisey shehar ke mutalliq suna hai jiski eik janib khushki hai aur eik taraf samandar hai? '' unhoney arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! ji haan , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qiyamat qaaim nahin hogi yahan tak ke bano Is-haq ke sattar hazar afrad wahan jihad karengey , jab wo wahan pahunch kar padaaw dalengey to wo na to aslaha se ladengey aur na teer andazi karengey ''wo (la Ilaah illallah wallahu-Akbar)'' padhengey to uski eik janib gir padeygi.'' Saur bin Yazid raawi bayan kartey hain, main nahin janta magar Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne us janib ke mutalliq farmaya jo samandar ki taraf hai, phir wo dusri martaba : ''(la Ilaah illallah wallahu-akbar)'' padhengey to uski dusri janib bhi gir padeygi, phir wo teesri martaba ''la Ilaah illallah wallahu-Akbar'' padhengey to wo (shehar) unke liye khol diya jaeyga to wo is mein dakhil hongey aur maale-ghanimat hasil karengey , wo maale-ghanimat taqseem kar rahey hongey ke eik zor daar aawaz unhen sunai deygi ke dajjaal ka zuhoor ho chuka hai, chunanche wo her chiz chhod kar wapis aa jaeyngey.'' rawahu Muslim."
5424,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''baitul-Maqdis ki abadi, yasrab ki barbadi ke waqt hogi, aur yasrab ki kharabi badi jang ke waqt hogi, aur badi jang Fateh Qustuntuniya ke waqt hogi, aur Qustuntuniya ki Fateh dajjaal ke nikalney ke waqt hogi.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
5425,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''badi jang, Qustuntuniya ki Fateh aur khurooj (bagawat) dajjaal saat maah mein hoga.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
5426,Hazrat Abdullah bin basar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jange-azeem aur shehar ki Fateh ke beech chhe saal ka waqfa hoga jabkey dajjaal ka zuhoor saatwen saal hoga.'' Abu-Dawood aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees ziyada sahih hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood.
5427,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain : qarib hai ke musalmanon ko Madina tak mahsoor (ghera band) kar diya jaey yahan tak ke unki sab se door wali sarhad salaah hogi. aur salaah khaibar ke qarib hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood.
5428,"Hazrat Zoo-Mikhbar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''an-qareeb tum (musalmano !) roomiyon se muahida aman karogey, tum aur wo apney peechhey eik dushman se jang karogey, tumhari madad ki jaeygi aur tum maale-ghanimat hasil karogey aur tum salaamat rahogey, phir tum wapis aao gey yahan tak ke tum sarsabz satah murtafaa' par utrogey to esaiyon (roomiyon) mein se eik shakhs saleeb buland kerega aur kahega saleeb ghalib aa gaee , is par eik musalman shakhs ghussey mein aa kar us (saleeb) ko tod dalega us waqt Romi ehad tod dengey aur wo jang ke liye jama hongey.'' aur baaz raawiyon ne ye izafa naqal kiya hai : ''tab musalman apney aslaha ki taraf daudengey aur wo qitaal karengey, Allah us jamaat ko shahadat ke ea'zaar se nawazeyga.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
5429,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tak Habshi tum se ched-chhad na karen tum bhi un se ched-chhadna na karo, kyonkey Kaba ka khazana bareek pindliyon wala Habshi hi nikalega.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
5430,"Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke eik sahabi se riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : ''tum habshiyon ko chhodey rakho jab tak wo tumhen chhodey rakhen aur (usi tarah) jab tak turak tumhen chhodey rakhen tum bhi unko chhodey rakho.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Nasai."
5431,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se is hadees mein riwayat kartey hain, jis mein hai : ''chhoti aakhon waley yani turak tum se qitaal karengey.'' farmaya : ''tum teen martaba unhen dhakelogey yahan tak ke tum unhen jazeera Arab tak pahuncha dogey, pehli martaba dhakelne ke moqey , bhag janey waley bach jaeyngey, dusri martaba baaz bach jaeyngey aur baaz halak ho jaeyngey, jabkey teesri martaba wo halak kar diye jaeyngey.'' ya jaisey aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
5432,"Hazrat abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri ummat ke kuch log nehar ke paas humwaar nashebi zamin par padaaw dalengey jisey wo Basra ke naam se jaanengey, aur us nehar ko dajla ke naam se yad kya jaeyga, is par eik pul hoga, uskey rehney waley bahut hongey, aur wo musalmanon ke shehron mein se hoga, aur jab aakhiri door hoga to bano qantura aaeyngey, jo chhodey chehron aur chhoti aakhon waley hongey, yahan tak ke wo nehar ke kinarey padaaw dalengey aur wo (Basra waley) teen girohon mein taqseem ho jaeyngey, eik giroh gaey ki dumein pakad lega aur wo jangalon mein (kheti baadi keren) gey , aur wo halak ho jaeyngey, eik giroh apni jaanon ke liye aman hasil kar lengey aur wo bhi halak ho jaeyngey, aur eik giroh apni aulad ko apni pusht ke peechey kar lengey aur wo un se qitaal karengey aur yehi shuda hain.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
5433,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Anas ! log shehar abad karengey aur un mein se eik shehar hai jisey Basra kaha jaeyga, agar tum wahan se guzro ya tum wahan jaao to uski shor wali zameen, ghaas wali zameen, uskey nakhlistan, uskey bazaron aur uskey hukmranon ke darwazon se bachtey rehna (mazkura jagahon par na jana), aur tum uskey atraaf mein rehna kyonkey is mein zamin ka dhansna hoga, aandhiyan aur zalzaley aaeyngey, wahan log raat ko soeyngey to subh ke waqt wo bandar aur khinzir bin jaeyngey.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
5434,"Hazrat Saleh bin Dirham bayan kartey hain, ham Haj ke liye rawana huye, to eik aadmi ne hamen kaha : tumharey paas eik basti hai jisey abla kaha jata hai? ham ne kaha : haan! usney kaha : tum mein se kon mujhey zamanat deta hai ke wo meri khatir masjid ishaar mein do ya chaar rakatein padhega, aur wo kahega ke ye ( rakatein) Abu-Hurera ke liye hain, maine apney dost abul-Qasim (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''be-shak Allah azz-w-jall roze-qiyamat masjid ishaar se shaheed uthaeyga, unke ilawa Badr ke shaheedon ke sath koi aur khada nahin hoga.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood . Abu-Dawood aur unhoney farmaya : ye masjid nehar ke kinarey waqey hai, aur ham abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees : '' ke musalmanon ke khemey . . . . . .'' ( baab zikr Yaman w Sham) mein inshaAllah Taala zikr karengey ."
5435,"Hazrat Shaqiq, Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney farmaya : ham umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas they to unhoney farmaya : ''tum mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se fitney ke mutalliq marwi (bayan) hadees kon yad rakhta hai? maine kaha : main yad rakhta hun jis tarah aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya tha. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : sunao! tum to badey dilair ho, aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kaisey farmaya tha? maine kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''aadmi ke liye uskey ehle w ayaal, uska maal, uski jaan, uski aulad aur uska padosi fitna w aazmaaish hain, jabkey roza, Namaz, sadqa aur neki ka hukm karna , burai se rokna uska kaffara hai.'' (us par) umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : meri ye murad nahin thi, meri murad to wo ( fitna ( hai jo samandar ki mojon ki tarah umad aaeyga , wo bayan kartey hain, maine arz kya, ameerul-momeneen! aap ko us se kya sarokaar? kyonkey uskey aur aap ke darmiyan band darwaza hai, unhoney kaha : wo darwaza khol diya jaeyga ya tod diya jaeyga ? wo bayan kartey hain, maine kaha : nahin, balke wo tod diya jaeyga, unhoney farmaya : phir ye uskey ziyada laaiq hai ke wo kabhi band na kya jaeyga . raawi bayan kartey hain, ham ne Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : kya umr (Raziallahu anhu) us darwazey ke mutalliq jantey they? unhoney kaha : haan, jaisey raat ke baad din aaney ka ilm hota hai, be-shak maine usey hadees bayan ki jis mein koi ghalati w Ibhaam nahin, raawi bayan kartey hain, ham ne khof ki wajeh se Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se us darwazey ke mutalliq daryaft nahin kya, ham ne Masruq se kaha ke aap Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se poochen, unhoney un se puchha to unhoney farmaya : wo umr hain. muttafaq aleh."
5436,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Qustuntuniya ki Fateh , qiyamat ke sath (yani qarib ( hogi .'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi ."
5437,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : '' alaamaat qiyamat mein se hai ke ilm uth jaeyga, jihalat ziyada ho jaeygi, zina kasrat se hoga, sharab noshi ziyada ho jaeygi, mard kam ho jaeyngey aur aurten ziyada ho jaeyngi yahan tak ke pachas aurton ke liye eik muntazim hoga.'' muttafaq aleh. eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''ilm kam ho jaeyga aur jihalat ghalib aa jaeygi.''"
5438,"Hazrat Jabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''qiyamat se pehley ( Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf jhooti baaten mansub karney waley ( kazaab hongey, tum un se mohtaat rehna .'' rawahu Muslim ."
5439,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, is beech mein ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) guftgu farma rahey they ke achcha eik Erabi (dehati) aaya to usney arz kya : qiyamat Kab aaeygi ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab amanat zaya ho jaey to phir qiyamat ka intizar kar .'' usney arz kya : uska zaya karna kaisey hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab maamlat naa-ahal logon ke supurd kar diye jaeyn to phir qiyamat ka intizar kar .'' Bukhari ."
5440,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qiyamat qaaim nahin hogi yahan tak ke maal ziyada ho jaeyga aur uski khub rel-pel hogi ke aadmi apni Zakat ka maal lekar niklega lekin usey wasul karney wala koi nahin milega aur yahan tak ke sar-zamine-arab sarsabz w shadab aur behti nehron wali wadi bin jaeygi.'' rawahu Muslim. Muslim hi ki eik dusri riwayat mein farmaya : ''Madina ki abadi abaab ya yahaab tak pahunch jaeygi .''"
5441,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aakhiri zamaney main eik khalifa hoga, wo maal taqseem kerega, aur usey ginega nahin.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai, farmaya : ''meri ummat ke aakhir par eik khalifa hoga jo chullu bhar-bhar kar maal dega aur wo usey gin-gin kar nahin dega.'' rawahu Muslim ."
5442,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qarib hai ke Furaat apney soney ke khazaney zahir kar dey, us waqt jo mojud ho wo us se kuch na ley.'' muttafaq aleh."
5443,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qiyamat qaaim nahin hogi yahan tak ke faraat se soney ka pahad zahir kar diya jaeyga, log is par jhagdengey to her so mein se ninnanwey qatl kar diye jaeyngey aur un mein se her shakhs kahega : main ummid karta hun ke wo najat paney wala main hun.'' rawahu Muslim ."
5444,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''zameen soney chaandi ke sutonon ke manind apney khazaney ugal degi to qatil aaeyga aur) afsos ke sath ( kahega, maine is wajeh se qatl kya tha, qata-rehmi karney wala aaeyga to wo kahega maine iski khatir apney rishtedaaron se natey todey, chor aaeyga aur kahega is wajeh se mera haath kaat diya gaya, phir wo usey chhod jaeyngey aur wo is mein se kuch bhi nahin lengey.'' rawahu Muslim ."
5445,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai! qiyamat qaaim nahin hogi yahan tak ke aadmi qabr ke paas se guzrey ga to wo is par lot-pot hoga (letega), aur kahega : kaash! ke us qabr waley ki jagah mein hota, aur wo ye baat Deen ki wajeh se nahin balke fitnon aur aazmaeshon ki wajeh se kahega.'' rawahu Muslim ."
5446,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qiyamat qaaim nahin hogi yahan tak ke sar-zameene-hijaaz se aag niklegi aur wo Basra (shaam ka eik shehar) mein oonton ki gardanon ko roshan kar degi.'' muttafaq aleh."
5447,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''alaamaate-qiyamat mein se pehli nishani aag hai jo logon ko mashriq se maghrib ki taraf jama kar degi.'' Bukhari .
5448,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qiyamat qaaim nahin hogi yahan tak ke zamana qarib aa jaeyga to saal mahiney ki tarah, mahina Jumey ( saat din ( ki tarah, Juma (yani hafta ( din ki tarah, din ghantey ki tarah aur ghanta aag ke sholay ki tarah hoga .'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
5449,"Hazrat Abdullah bin hawala (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamen maale-ghanimat hasil karney ke liye pedal bheja, ham maale-ghanimat hasil kiye baghair wapis aaye aur aapney hamarey chehron par mashaqqat ke aasaar dekhey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamen khitab farmaney ke liye khadey huey aur dua farmaai : ''aey Allah ! unhen merey supurd na kar, mein un se ziyada zaeef hunga, unhen unki jinnon ke supurd na kar wo us se aajiz aa jaeyngey aur unhen logon ke hawaley na kar wo apney aap ko un par tarjeeh dengey.'' aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apna dast Mubarak merey sar par rakha, aur farmaya : ''ibne-hawala! jab tum dekho ke khilaafat arze-muqaddas (mulke-shaam) muntaqil ho gaee hai to phir (samajh lena) zalzaley, gham aur alaamaat qiyamat qarib aa chuki hain, aur us waqt qiyamat logon ke is qadr qarib hogi jis qadr mera haath terey sar ke qarib hai.'' Abu-Dawud, aur iski sanad Hasan hai, aur haakim ne usey apni sahih mein riwayat kya hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
5450,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab maale-fai / maale-ghanimat ko dolat , amanat ko maale-ghanimat aur Zakat ko tawaan samjha jaey, ilm deeni maqaasid ke ilawa dunyawi maqaasid ke liye hasil kya jaey, aadmi apni ehliya ka itaat guzar bin jaey aur apni walida ki nafarmani karey, wo apney dost ko muqarrab banaey aur apney walid ko door rakhey, masaajid mein aawazen buland honey lagen, qabiley ka sab se ziyada ahmaq shakhs qabiley ka sardar bin jaey, qom ka zimmedar w muntazim unka sab se ziyada razeel shakhs ho, aadmi ki uskey shar ke khof ki wajeh se izzat ki jaey, gaaney waliyan aur aalaate-mosiqi (musical instruments) aam ho jaeyn, sharab noshi ki jaey, aur is ummat ke baad waley log apney pehley logon (yani salaf) par laan-taan karen to us waqt tum surkh aandhiyon , zalzalon , zamin mein dhansney, chehron ke maskh ho janey, aasman se pathar barasney aur deegar nishaniyon ke is tarah musalsal aaney ka intizar karo jis tarah haar ki dori toot jaey to phir moti lagataar girtey hain.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5451,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab meri ummat pandrah (burey) kaam karegi to is par bula nazil hogi, aapney wo kaam shumar kiye lekin Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye zikr nahin kya ke ''ilm deeni maqaasid ke ilawa hasil kya jaeyga.'' farmaya : '' apney dost se husne-suluk kerega aur walid se jafa kerega.'' aur farmaya : ''sharab noshi ki jaey aur resham pehna jaey.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
5452,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''duniya khatam nahin hogi yahan tak ke merey ehle bait se mera ham naam shakhs Arbon ka badshah bin jaeyga.'' aur Abu-Dawood ki riwayat mein hai farmaya : ''agar duniya ka sirf eik hi din baqi reh gaya to Allah us din ko lamba kerega yahan tak ke Allah is mein merey ehle bait se eik aadmi bhejega jis ka naam merey naam jaisa aur uskey walid ka naam merey walid ke naam jaisa hoga, wo zamin ko adl w insaf se bhar dega jis tarah wo zulm w sitam se bhari hui thi.'' rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood."
5453,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''Mehdi meri Itrat, Fatima (Raziallahu anhu) ki aulad se hoga.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
5454,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Mehdi meri aulad se hongey, jo ke kushada peshani aur buland naak waley hongey, wo zamin ko adl w insaf se bhar dega jis tarah wo zulm w sitam se bhari hui thi, wo saat saal hukumat kerega.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
5455,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) Mehdi ke qissey ke barey mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aadmi uskey paas aaeyga to wo kahega : Mehdi! mujhey ata karo, mujhey ata karo, farmaya : wo uskey kapdey ko bhar dengey aur wo shakhs usey uthaney se qaasir rahega .'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
5456,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat karti hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''badshah ki maut ke waqt ikhtilaf ho jaeyga, ehle Madina se eik aadmi nikal kar Makka ki taraf bhag khada hoga, ehle-Makka se kuchh log uskey paas aaeyngey to wo usey (uskey ghar sey) bahar laeyngey, wo napasand karta hoga, lekin wo rukn (Hajre-Aswad) aur maqame Ibrahim ke darmiyan uski baiat karengey, Sham ki taraf se (us se ladney ke liye) uski taraf eik lashkar rawana kiya jaeyga, lekin us lashkar ko Makka aur Madina ke darmiyan maqame Beda par dhansa diya jaeyga, jab log ye soorate haal dekhengey to Sham ke abdaal (ibadat guzar) aur Iraaq ke behtareen ashkhaas (log) uskey paas aaeyngey to wo uski baiat kar lengey , phir Quraish se eik aadmi zahir hoga jiska nanihal kalb qabiley se honga, wo (kalbi) un (baiat karney walon) ki taraf eik lashkar bhejeingey to wo (baiat karney waley) un par ghalib aa jaeyngey, aur ye kalb ka lashkar hoga, aur wo (Mehdi) un mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sunnat ke mutabiq amal karengey, Islam zamin par Sabit aur qaaim ho jaeyga, wo saat saal rahengey , phir wafat pa jaeyngey, aur musalman unki Namaze janaza padhengey.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
5457,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik balaa ka zikr kiya jo is ummat ko pahuncheygi, yahan tak ke koi bhi aadmi zulm se koi jaey panah nahin paeyga , Allah meri aulad aur merey ehale bait se eik aadmi mab-us (bhejega) farmaeyga , aur uskey zariey zamin ko adl aur insaf se bhar dega jis tarah ye zulm aur sitam se bhari hui thi, aasman ke rehney waley aur zamin ke baasi us se razi ho jaeyngey . aasman mooslaa-dhaar barish barsaeyga aur zamin apni tamam nabatat (paid paudhe) uga deygi yahan tak ke zinda afrad faut shuda afrad ki zindagiyon ki khahish karengey (ke kaash! wo bhi zinda hotey) wo (Mehdi) us haalat (adl aur insaf) mein saat , aath ya nau saal zinda rahengey.'' rawahu al-Hakim."
5458,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Warain Nahr se Haris naami shakhs ka zuhoor hoga, wo kheti karney wala hoga, uskey awwal dastey par Mansoor naami shakhs hoga, wo Aale Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko jagah aur ikhtiyar aur iqtidar dega jis tarah Quraish ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko iqtidar aur ikhtiyar diya, uski madad karna ya uski baat manna her momin par wajib hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
5459,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! qiyamat qaaim nahin hogi yahan tak ke darindey insanon se kalam karengey , aur yahan tak ke bandey se uskey kodey ka sar aur uskey jootey ka tasma kalam karega aur uski raan usko us kaam ke mutalliq bataeygi jo uskey baad uskey ehal ne kiya hoga.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5460,"Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''alaamaat (qiyamat) do sau (saal) ke baad hongi.'' rawahu ibne-Maja."
5461,"Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum khuraasaan ki taraf se siyah jhandey aatey dekho to unka istaqbal karo, kyonkey un mein Allah ka khalifa Mehdi hoga.'' (rawahu Ahmed aur al-Behaqi)."
5462,"Hazrat Abu Is'haq bayan kartey hain, Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya, aur unhoney apney bete Hasan (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf dekha to farmaya : be-shak mera ye beta saiyed hai jis tarah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uska naam rakha, aur an-qareeb uski salb se eik aadmi nikleyga uska naam tumharey Nabi ke naam par hoga, wo akhlaq aur seerat mein unke mushabeh hoga, aur wo nuqoosh aur qad w qaamat mein unke mushabeh nahin hoga, phir qissa zikr kiya ke wo zamin ko adl se bhar dega.'' Abu-Dawud, aur unhoney qissa zikr nahin kiya. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
5463,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke dure-khilaafat ke us saal jis saal umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne wafat pai , tiddi ma'doom ho gaee to us se wo bahut ghamgin ho gaey, unhoney eik sawar Yamen ki taraf , eik Iraq ki taraf aur eik sawar Sham ki taraf bheja ta ke wo tiddi ke mutalliq daryaft karen ke aaya wo kahin nazar aai hai, Yamen ki taraf se sawar mutthi mein tiddiyan lekar aaya aur unhen aap ( umr (Raziallahu anhu)) ke samney phela diya, jab unhoney unhen dekha to ( khushi sey) na'ra takbir buland kya, aur farmaya : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''be-shak Allah azz-w-jall ne hazar qism ke haiwaan paida farmaai , un mein se chhe so samandar mein hain, aur chaar so khushki mein , aur un mein se sab se pehley tiddiyan halak hongi , jab tiddiyan halak ho jaeyngi to uskey baad haar ki dori tootney ke baad motiyon ke girney ki tarah baqi ummaten ( iqsaam ( halak hongi .'' ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
5464,"Hazrat Huzefa bin Usaid ghifaari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey paas tashrif laye to ham aapas mein baat cheet kar rahey they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum kya baaten kar rahey ho?'' unhoney arz kya, ham qiyamat ka tazkira kar rahey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo qaaim nahin hogi yahan tak ke tum us se pehley das nishaniyan dekh lo, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne dhoein, dajjaal, janwer ke nikalney , Suraj ke maghrib se tulu honey , Esa bin Maryam (Alaihissalam) ke tashrif laney , yajooj Majuj ke nikalney , teen baar zamin ke dhansney : eik baar mashriq main eik baar maghrib mein aur eik baar jazeera Arab mein dhansney ka zikr farmaya aur un ( das ( mein se aakhiri nishani ka zikr farmaya ke aag Yamen ki taraf se niklegi wo logon ko unke hashr ke maidan ki taraf haank kar ley jaeygi.'' aur eik riwayat mein hai : ''adn ke aakhiri kinarey se aag zahir hogi, wo logon ko hashr ke maidan ki taraf haankegi.'' aur dusri riwayat mein daswin nishani ke mutalliq hai : ''wo hawa hogi jo logon ko samandar mein phenk degi.'' rawahu Muslim ."
5465,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' nek aamaal karney mein jaldi karo, ( alaamaat qiyamat ke zuhoor se pehley jo ke) chhe hain, dhuwan, dajjaal, daabbatul-arz aur Suraj ka maghrib se tulu hona, neez wo aam fitna ( maut ( jo aam logon ko halak kar dega aur khas fitna jo tumharey khas ko fana kar dega.'' rawahu Muslim ."
5466,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''alaamaate-qiyamat mein se pehli (samaawi) alamat Suraj ka maghrib se tulu hona hai, aur chaasht ke waqt daabba (haiwaan) ka logon ke samney nikalna hai, un dono mein se jo bhi apney sath waley se pehley nikal aaya to doosra uskey peechey qarib hi hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
5467,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' teen nishaniyan, jab unka zuhoor ho jaeyga to '' us waqt kisi shakhs ka eman lana uskey liye nafamand nahin hoga b-sharte-ke wo us se pehley eman na laya ho ya usney haalate-emaan mein nek kaam na kiye hon.'' Suraj ka maghrib se tulu hona, dajjaal aur daabbatul-arz ka nikalna .'' rawahu Muslim ."
5468,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum jantey ho ke Suraj ghurub honey ke baad kahan jata hai? ''maine arz kya, Allah aur uskey Rasool behtar jantey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo jata hai yahan tak ke arsh ke nichey sajda rez ho kar) mashriq se tulu honey ki) ijazat talab karta hai, usey ijazat de-di jati hai, aur qarib hai ke wo sajda karey aur wo us se qubul na kya jaey, wo ijazat talab karey aur usey ijazat na di jaey, aur usey kaha jaey, jahan se aaye ho wahin chaley jaao , wo maghrib se tulu hoga, aur ye Allah Taala ka farman hai : '' Suraj apni qarar gaah ki taraf chal raha hai.'' farmaya : '' uski qarar gaah arsh ke nichey hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
5469,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : '' Adam (Alaihissalam) ki takhleeq aur qiyame-qiyamat ke darmiyan dajjaal se badh kar koi fitna nahin.'' rawahu Muslim."
5470,"Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak Allah tum par makhfii nahin, bila-shuba Allah Taala kaana nahin, jabkey Masih dajjaal ki daain aankh kaani hogi , goya uski aankh aisi hogi ke angoor ka utha hua dana ho.'' muttafaq aleh."
5471,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''her Nabi ne apni ummat ko kaaney kazzaab (dajjaal) se daraya aur aagah farmaya, sun lo! wo kaana hai, jabkey tumhara rab kaana nahin, aur uski dono aakhon ke darmiyan ک .  . ر ( kafir ( likha hua hoga .'' muttafaq aleh."
5472,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''suno! main dajjaal ke mutalliq tumhen eik baat batata hun, jo kisi Nabi ne apni qom ko bayan nahin ki ke wo ( dajjaal ( kaana hoga, wo aaeyga to uskey sath jannat ke misl hogi aur aag ke misl hogi , wo jiskey mutalliq ye kahega ke ye jannat hai to wo aag hogi aur main tumhen us (ke fitney ( se isi tarah darata hun, jis tarah Nuh (Alaihissalam) ne uskey mutalliq apni qom ko daraya tha.'' muttafaq aleh."
5473,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' be-shak dajjaal ka zuhoor hoga aur uskey sath pani aur aag hogi , jisey log pani samjhengey wo aag hogi wo jalaeygi , aur jisey log aag samjhen gey wo thanda sheereen pani hoga, tum mein se jo aisi surat dekhey to wo us chiz mein waqey ho jisey wo aag samajhta ho, kyonkey wo to sheereen khushgawar pani hai.'' aur Imam Muslim ne ye alfaz naqal kiye hain : '' be-shak dajjaal ki eik aankh nahin hogi , uski ( aankh ( par mota nakhun hoga, aur uski dono aakhon ke darmiyan kafir likha hoga, aur usey her momin padh lega chahey likhna padhna janta ho ya na janta ho.'' muttafaq aleh."
5474,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''dajjaal baain aankh se kaana hoga, uskey ( jism par) baal ghaney hongey, uskey sath uski jannat aur uski aag hogi , uski aag jannat hogi aur uski jannat haqiqat mein aag hogi .'' rawahu Muslim ."
5475,"Hazrat Nawaas bin Samaan (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne dajjaal ka zikr kya to farmaya : ''agar wo meri mojudgi mein nikal aaya to phir main tumhari taraf se us se jhagda karunga , aur agar wo us waqt nikley jabke main tum mein na hon to phir her shakhs apni khatir us se jhagda kerega, aur Allah her eik musalman par muhafiz w muawin hai, be-shak wo ( dajjaal ( jawan hoga, uskey baal ghoongariyaaley hongey, uski aankh uthi hui hogi, goya main usey Abdul-Uzza bin qatan se tashbih deta hun, tum mein se jo shakhs usey pa ley to wo is par Sura kahaf ki ibtidaai (shuruati) aayaat padhey , kyonkey wo tumharey liye uskey fitney se aman hain, wo Sham aur Iraq ke darmiyan eik raah par nikalney wala hai, wo daain baain fasad machaeyga, Allah ke bando ! Sabit rehna.'' ham ne arz kya : Allah ke Rasool! wo zamin mein kitni muddat thehrega? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' chaalis din , eik din saal ki tarah , eik ( doosra ( din mahiney ki tarah , aur eik ( teesra ( din Juma ( saat din ( ki tarah hoga, jabkey uskey baqi dinon tumharey dinon ki tarah hongey .'' ham ne arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! kya wo din jo saal ki tarah hoga to kya us main eik din ki Namaz padhna hamarey liye kafi hoga ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' nahin, balke tum uskey liye uska andaza kar lena .'' ham ne arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! uski zamin par raftaar kya hogi ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' barish ki tarah jiskey peechey hawa aati hai, wo logon ke paas aaeyga , unhen dawat dega to wo is par eman ley aaeyngey , wo aasman ko hukm dega to wo barish barsaeyga aur zamin ko hukm dega to wo anaj ugaaeygi, unke charney waley janwer Sham ko wapis aaeyngey to unki kohanein pehley se ziyada lambi, unke than doodh se bharey hongey aur unki kokhein bahar nikli hongi, phir wo kuch logon ke paas aaeyga, wo unhen dawat dega, wo uski baat qubul nahin karengey, wo unke paas se chala jaeyga to wo qehat saali ka shikar ho jaeyngey : unke haath amwaal se khaali ho jaeyngey, aur wo eik weeraaney se guzrega to usey kahega, apney khazaney nikalo, to us ( weeraaney (ke khazaney us (dajjaal) ke peechey is tarah chalengey jis tarah shehad ki makkhiyaan apney sardaron ke peechey chalti hain, phir wo bharpur jawan aadmi ko bulaeyga, aur talwaar maar kar uskey do tukdey kar dega, jis tarah hadaf par nishana bazi ki jati hai, phir wo usko bulaeyga to wo uski taraf mutawajjeh hoga aur chamaktey chehrey ke sath muskraata hua apni usi pehli haalat par ho jaeyga . achcha Allah Masih bin Maryam ko uthaaeyga to wo Zaafran rang ke jodey mein dimashq ke mashriq mein minaara baizaa par nuzool farmaeyngey, wo do farishton ke paron par haath rakhey hongey, jab wo apna sar jhukaeyngey to us se qatrey girengey, aur jab wo usey uthaeyngey to us se moti ke daney tapkengey, aur jo kafir unke saans ki hawa paeyga to wo halak ho jaeyga, aur unka saans hade-nigah tak pahuncheyga, wo (Esa (Alaihissalam)) usey talash karengey yahan tak ke wo usey baab Ludd par paeyngey aur usey qatl kar dengey, phir Esa (Alaihissalam) ke paas wo log aaeyngey jinhen Allah ne us se bacha liya hoga, chunanche wo unke chehrey saaf karengey aur wo unke jannat mein darjaat ke mutalliq unhen bataeyngey, wo usi beech mein hongey jab Allah Taala Esa (Alaihissalam) ki taraf wahi bhejega ke maine apney aisey bandey zahir kiye hain, un se qitaal ki kisi mein taqat nahin, aap merey bandon ko taur ki taraf ley jaeyn . chunanche Allah yajooj Majuj ko bhejega, wo her buland jagah se dodey aaeyngey unke pehley log Buhera tabriya par guzrengey to wo uska sara pani pi jaeyngey, jab unka aakhiri aadmi wahan se guzrega to wo kahega : yahan kisi waqt pani hota tha ! phir wo chaltey jaeyngey yahan tak ke wo jabale-khamr yani jabale-baitul-Maqdis tak pahunchengey to wo kahengey : ham zamin walon ko to qatl kar chukey aao! ab ham aasman walon ko qatl karen, wo aasman ki taraf teer chalaeyngey, to Allah unke teeron ko khoon aalud haalat mein un par lota dega, Allah ke Nabi aur uskey sathi rok liye jaeyngey yahan tak ke us roz bail ka sar unke yahan so Dinar se behtar hoga, Allah ke Nabi Esa (Alaihissalam) aur unke sathi ( Allah ki taraf ( raghbat karengey. to Allah unki gardanon mein keeda paida kar dega to wo eik jaan ki maut ki tarah sab halak ho jaeyngey, phir Allah ke Nabi Esa (Alaihissalam) aur unke sathi (pahad sey) nichey utrengey, wo zamin par baalisht barabar jagah nahin paeyngey magar wo unki charbi aur badboo se bharpur hogi, phir Allah ke Nabi (Alaihissalam) aur unke sathi Allah ke huzur dua karengey to wo bakhti oont ki kohaanon ki tarah perindey un par bhejega to wo unhen utha kar jahan Allah chahega, phenk aaeyngey.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''wo unhen nehbal ke maqam par phenk aaeyngey, musalman unki kamanon, unke teeron aur unke tarkashon ko saat saal jalaatey rahengey, phir Allah Taala barish barsaeyngey ke wo her ghar par barseygi (chahey wo pathar se banaya gaya ho ya koi khema ho), wo (barish) zamin ko dho dalegi, yahan tak ke usey shishey ki tarah kar degi, phir zamin se kaha jaeyga, apney samraat ugaao! aur apni barkaat lota do!, us din puri jamaat faqat eik anaar se sair ho jaeygi aur uskey chhilkey se saya hasil karengey, aur doodh mein barkat dal di jaeygi, yahan tak ke oontni ka doodh logon ki eik jamaat ke liye kafi hoga, gaey ka doodh logon ke qabiley ke liye kafi hoga, bakri ka doodh chhotey qabiley ke liye kafi hoga, wo usi haalat mein hongey ke Allah pakizah hua bhejeyga wo unki baghlon ke nichey lagegi aur wo her momin aur her musalman ki rooh qabz kar legi, aur shareer log baqi reh jaeyngey, wo us waqt gadhon ki tarah elania zina karengey, aur aisey logon par qiyamat qaaim hogi.'' Muslim. albatta dusri riwayat : wo unka ye kehna : '' wo unko nehbal mein phenk degi.'' se lekar '' saat saal tak.'' usey Imam Tirmizi ne riwayat kya hai. rawahu Muslim w Tirmizi."
5476,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''dajjaal niklega to mominon mein se eik aadmi uski taraf rukh kerega to dajjaal ke muhafiz w chaukidaar usey milengey to wo usey kahengey, kahan ka irada hai? wo kahega : main uski taraf ja raha hun jis ka zuhoor hua hai, wo usey kahengey : kya tum hamarey rab par eman nahin rakhtey ? wo kahega : hamarey rab ke baraaheen w dalaeyl makhfii nahin, wo kahengey : usey qatl kar do, phir wo eik doosrey se kahengey : kya tumharey rab ne tumhen mana nahin kya ke tum ne uski ghair mojudgi mein kisi ko qatl nahin karna? lihaza wo usey dajjaal ke paas ley chalengey, chunanche jab wo momin shakhs usey dekhega to wo kahega : logo! ye wohi dajjaal hai jis ka Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne zikr kya tha.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''dajjaal uskey mutalliq hukm dega to uska sar phod diya jaeyga, wo kahega : usey pakdo aur uska sar phod do (eik dusri riwayat mein hai : usey chit lita do), aur uski pusht aur pet par bahut ziyada maara jaeyga.'' farmaya : ''wo kahega : kya tum mujh par eman nahin latey?'' farmaya : ''wo shakhs kahega : to Masih kazaab hai.'' farmaya : ''us shakhs ke mutalliq hukm diya jaeyga to uskey sar par aari chala di jaeygi yahan tak ke uskey do tukdey kar diye jaeyngey .'' farmaya : '' phir dajjaal un do tukdon ke beech chalega, phir usey kahega : khadey ho jaao to wo sahih salaamat khada ho jaeyga, wo phir us se puchega : kya tum mujh par eman latey ho? wo jawab dega : tumharey mutalliq meri baseerat mein izafa hi hua hai.'' farmaya : '' phir wo ( aadmi ( kahega : logo ! wo merey baad kisi shakhs ke sath aisey nahin kerega .'' farmaya : ''dajjaal usey zibeh karney ke liye pakdega, to uski gardan aur hansli ke darmiyan tanba bana diya jaeyga, lihaza wo usey qatl nahin kar sakega.'' farmaya : ''wo usey dono haathon aur uski dono taangon se pakad kar usey phenk dega, log samjhengey ke usney usey aag ki taraf phenka hai, halanke usey to jannat mein dal diya gaya hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''rabbul-aalameen ke nazdik ye shakhs shahadat ke sab se azeem martabey par faaiz hoga.'' rawahu Muslim ."
5477,"Hazrat Umme-Shareek (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''log dajjaal se bhag kar pahadon par ja pahuncheingey.'' Umme-Shareek (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! us waqt Arab kahan hongey? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo (us waqt) qaleel (kam) hongey.'' rawahu Muslim."
5478,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Asfahaan ke sattar hazar Yahudi dajjaal ki itaat karengey , un par siyah chadaren hongi.'' rawahu Muslim."
5479,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Dajjaal aaeyga aur uskey liye Madina ki ghaatiyon mein dakhil hona haram hai, chunanche wo Madina ke qarib shor wali zamin par padaaw daleyga, phir eik aadmi uskey paas jaeyga jo ke (us waqt) sab se behtareen shakhs hoga, wo kahega : main gawahi deta hun ke to wohi Dajjaal hai jiskey mutalliq Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein bayan farmaya tha. Dajjaal kahega : mujhey bataao agar main isko qatl kar dun, phir isey zinda kar dun to kya tum merey mamley mein shak karogey? wo kahengey nahin, wo usko qatl kerega, phir usey zinda kar dega to wo kahega : Allah ki qism ! terey mutalliq mujhey aaj pehley se ziyada baseerat hasil ho gaee hai, phir Dajjaal usey qatl karna chahega , lekin wo us (ke qatl karney) par qadir nahin ho sakega.'' muttafaq aleh."
5480,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Dajjaal Madiney ke iraday se mashriq ki taraf se aaeyga yahan tak ke wo uhad pahad ke peechhey qiyam karega , phir farishtey uska chehra Sham ki taraf pher dengey , aur wo wahin halak hoga.'' muttafaq aleh."
5481,"Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Madina (uskey logon ke dilon) mein Dajjaal ka roab dakhil nahin hoga, us din us (Madiney) ke saat darwazey hongey aur her darwazey par do farishtey muqarrar hongey.'' Bukhari."
5482,"Hazrat Fatima binte-Qais (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke manadi ko ye aelan kartey huey suna : Namaz jama karney wali hai, main masjid ki taraf gaee aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Namaz padhi , jab aap Namaz padh chukey to member par beth gaey aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hans rahey they, farmaya : ''tamam log apni apni jagahon par bethey rahen.'' phir farmaya : ''kya tumhen malum hai ke maine tumhen kis liye jama kiya hai? '' unhoney arz kiya, Allah aur uskey Rasool behtar jantey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ki qism ! maine tumhen kisi raghbat (maal ghanimat waghera deney) ke liye jama nahin kiya hai na kisi khof ki wajeh sey, balke maine tumhen isliye jama kiya hai ke Tameem Daari nasrani shakhs tha, wo aaya usney baiat ki aur musalman ho gaya usney mujhey wo baat bayan ki aur wo usi baat ke muwaafiq thi jo main tumhen Masih Dajjaal ke mutalliq bayan karta hun, usney mujhey bataya ke wo lakham aur juzaam qabiley ke tees afrad ke sath kashti mein sawar hua , mojen eik maah tak unhen samandar mein liye phirin (bahir kinarey par pahunchney ka moqey na mila) wo ghurub aaftaab ke waqt eik jazeerey ke qarib pahunch gaey, wo chhoti kashti mein beth kar jazeere mein dakhil huey to Kasir baalon wala eik haiwaan unhen mila , baalon ki kasrat ki wajeh se wo nahin jantey they ke uska aglaa hissey kon sa hai aur pichhlaa hissey kon sa hai? unhoney kaha teri tabahi ho, to kya chiz hai? usney arz kiya : main (Dajjaal ka ( jaasus hun, ham ne kaha jaasus se kya murad hai? usney kaha, tum girje mein us aadmi ki taraf chalo , kyonkey wo tumhen milney ka mushtaaq hai, unhoney (Tameem Daari) ne farmaya : jab usney us aadmi ke mutalliq hamein bataya to ham us (haiwaan) se dar gaey ke ye kahin shetan na ho, ham jaldi jaldi chaley yahan tak ke ham girjey mein dakhil ho gaey, to wahan eik azeem jussey wala insan tha, ham ne takhleeq aur mazbut ke lihaz se us jaisa insan pehley kabhi nahin dekha tha, wo zanjeeron mein jakdaa hua tha, uskey haath uski gardan ke sath bandhey huey they, aur uskey ghutnon aur takhnon ke beech lohey ki zanjeeren thin, ham ne kaha : teri tabahi ho, to kon hai? usney kaha : tum meri khabar (maloom karney) par to qudrat pa chukey ho, mujhey bataao ke tum kon ho? unhoney kaha : ham Arab log hain, ham eik kashti mein sawar huey to samandar ki mojen eik maah tak hamen idhar-udhar phairaati rahin, ham jazeerey mein dakhil huey to Kasir baalon wala eik janwer hamein mila to usney kaha : main jaasus hun, tum girjey mein mojud us shakhs ke paas jaao , lihaza ham jaldi jaldi terey paas pahunch gaey hain, lekin us jaasus se ham khaufzada huey ke kahin wo shetan na ho, usney kaha : tum mujhey beesaan ke nakhlistan ke barey mein bataao , kya wo phal deta hai? ham ne kaha, haan , usney kaha, suno ! qarib hai ke wo phal nahin dega , usney kaha : buhira tabriya ke mutalliq mujhey bataao ? kya is mein pani hai? ham ne kaha : is mein bahut ziyada pani hai, usney kaha : qarib hai ke uska pani khatam ho jaeyga, usney kaha : mujhey chashma zaghar ke mutalliq bataao kya chashmey mein pani hai, aur kya wahan rehney waley chashmey ke pani se kheti kartey hain? ham ne kaha : haan is mein pani bhi bahut hai, aur wahan ke rehney waley us pani se kheti bhi kartey hain, usney kaha : mujhey an-padh (arbon) ke Nabi ke mutalliq bataao usney kya kiya? ham ne usey bataya ke wo Makka chhod kar Madina tashrif ley aaye hain? usney kaha : kya Arbon ne us se ladaai ki hai? ham ne kaha : haan , usney kaha : unke sath kya kiya? ham ne usey bataya ke wo apney qarib ke Arbon par ghalib aa chukey hain, aur unhon (arbon) ne aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki itaat ikhtiyar kar li hai. usney kaha : suno ! agar wo unki itaat karen to unke haq mein yehi behtar hai aur main ab tumhen apney mutalliq batata hun ke main Masih Dajjaal hun, be-shak qarib hai ke mujhey nikalney ki ijazat di jaey to main nikal aaunga, main zamin par chalunga, aur main chaalis roz main zamin par Makka aur tayiba  (Madina) ke alawa her basti mein utroonga, wo dono mujh par haram hain. main jab bhi un dono mein se kisi eik mein dakhil honey ka irada karunga to eik farishta haath mein talwaar sunte huey merey samney aa jaeyga, aur wo is mein dakhil honey se mujhey rokeyga , aur uskey her raastey aur darwazey par farishtey hain jo uski hifazat kartey hain.'' Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya aur aapney member par chhadi maari : ye (yani Madina) tayiba hai, ye tayiba hai, ye tayiba hai. suno ! kya maine tumhen hadees suna di thi?'' logon ne arz kiya : ji haan (farmaya) ''suno ! wo Sham ke samandar mein hai ya wo Yamen ke samandar mein hai, nahin balke wo mashriq ki taraf se nikley ga.'' aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne jo ishara farmaya tha wo mashriq ki taraf tha. rawahu Muslim."
5483,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' aaj ki raat maine apney aap ko (khuwab mein) Kaba ke paas dekha, maine wahan gandumi rang ke eik aadmi ko dekha ke maine gandumi rang mein us se ziyada khoobsurat shakhs koi nahin dekha, uskey sar ke baal kanon ki lau tak they, maine kanon ki lo tak us se ziyada khoobsurat baal nahin dekhey , us shakhs ne un mein kanghi bhi ki hui thi, aur sar se pani ke qatrey gir rahey they, wo do aadmiyon ke kandhon ka sahara liye Baitullah ka tawaf kar raha tha, maine puchha , ye kon hai? unhoney bataya : ye Masih bin Maryam (Alaihissalam) hain.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''phir maine bahut hi ghoongariyaaley baalon waley shakhs ko dekha, uski daain aankh kaani thi, goya uski aankh ubhrey huey angoor ki tarah hai, aur wo ibne Qatan ke sath rehney waley logon ke jinhen maine dekha tha ziyada mushabeh hai, wo bhi do aadmiyon ke kandhon par haath rakh kar Baitullah ka tawaf kar raha tha, maine puchha : ye kon hai? unhoney kaha ye Masih Dajjaal hai.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Dajjaal ke mutalliq farmaya : ''wo surkh rang ka aadmi hai, uskey baal ghoongariyaaley hain, daain aankh se kaanaa hai, aur wo sab se ziyada ibne Qatan se mushaabihat rakhta hai.'' aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees : ''qiyamat qaaim nahin hogi yahan tak ke Suraj maghrib se tulu ho jaey.'' (باب الملاحم) mein bayan ho chuki hai aur ham an-qareeb ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees : '' Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) logon ko khitab karney ke liye khadey huey .'' Insha Allah Taala (باب قصۃ ابن الصیاد) mein zikr karengey. muttafaq aleh."
5484,"Hazrat Fatima binte-Qais (Raziallahu anhu) ne, Tameem Daari (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees ke mutalliq bayan kiya ke unhon (Tameem daari (Raziallahu anhu)) ne farmaya : ''main achcha eik aisi aurat ke paas se guzra jo apney baal khinch rahi thi, unhoney puchha : to kon hai? usney kaha : main jaasus hun, us mehal ki taraf jaao , main wahan gaya to wahan eik aadmi apney baal khinch raha hai, wo zanjeeron mein jakdaa hua hai uskey sath toq bhi hain, aur wo zamin aur aasman ke darmiyan kood raha hai, maine kaha : to kon hai? usney kaha : main Dajjaal hun.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
5485,"Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maine tumhen Dajjaal ke mutalliq hadees bayan ki yahan tak ke mujhey andesha hua ke tum nahin samajh sakey ho, be-shak Masih Dajjaal chhotey qad ka hai, uskey dono paaon mein uskey mamool se ziyada kushadgi hogi , baal ghoongariyaaley , kaanaa hoga, aankh ghayeb hogi , uski (doosri) aankh buland hogi na dhansi hogi , agar phir bhi tumhen mughaalta ho jaey to jaan lo ke tumhara rab kaanaa nahin.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
5486,"Hazrat Abu Ubeda bin Jarrah (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''Nooh (Alaihissalam) ke baad her Nabi (Alaihissalam) ne apni qom ko Dajjaal se daraya hai, aur main tumhen us se darata hun.'' aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein uska Taaruf : karaya , farmaya : ''an-qareeb koi jisney mujhey dekha hai ya mera kalam suna hai, usey pa lega.'' unhoney arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! us waqt hamarey dil kaisey hongey? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jaisey aaj hain ya (us sey) behtar.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
5487,"Hazrat Amr bin Hurais ne Abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki hai, unhoney kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein hadees bayan kartey huey farmaya : ''Dajjaal mashriqi sarzameen se nikleyga, jisey khuraasaan kaha jata hai, jo log uski ittiba karengey unke chehrey teh ba teh dhaal jaisey hongey.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5488,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Dajjaal ke mutalliq suney to wo us se door rahey, Allah ki qism ! aadmi uskey paas aaeyga jo khud ko momin samajhta hoga, lekin jin shub'haat ke sath Dajjaal bheja jaeyga wo unki wajeh se uski ittiba kerega.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
5489,"Hazrat Asma binte Yazid bin Sakan (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Dajjaal zamin par chaalis saal rahega , saal mahiney ki tarah , mahina Jumey (haftey yani saat din) ki tarah , Juma (yani hafta) din ki tarah aur din aag mein tinkey ke jal janey ki manind hoga.'' (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah)."
5490,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri ummat ke sattar hazar afrad Dajjaal ki ittiba karengey , unke saron par sabz (hara) siyah rang ke kapdey hongey.'' (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah)."
5491,"Hazrat Asma binte Yazid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) merey ghar mein they, aapney Dajjaal ka zikr kiya to farmaya : ''us se pehley teen qism ke qehat (sukhe) hongey, eik qehat ye hoga ke is mein aasman tihai barish rok lega , zamin apni tihai nabatat (paid paudhe) rok leygi , doosrey mein ye hoga ke aasman apni do tihai barish rok lega , zamin apni do tihai nabatat rok legi , aur teesrey mein aasman apni sari barish rok lega , aur zamin apni tamam nabatat rok leygi chaupaaon mein se koi khir wala baqi bachey ga na koi kuchli wala, sab halak ho jaeyngey, uska sab se shadeed fitna ye hoga ke wo Erabi (dehati) (dehati) ke paas aaeyga to kahega , mujhey bataao agar main tumharey oont ko zinda kar dun to kya tujhey yaqin nahin aaeyga ke main tumhara rab hun? wo kahega : kyon nahin, shetan uskey liye uskey oont ki surat ikhtiyar kar lega , to uskey than behtareen ho jaeyngey aur uski kohan bahut badi ho jaeygi.'' farmaya : ''wo (Dajjaal) doosrey aadmi ke paas aaeyga jis ka bhai aur walid wafat pa chukey hongey, to wo (usey) kahega , mujhey bataao agar main tumharey liye tumharey walid aur tumharey bhai ko zinda kar dun to kya tujhey yaqin nahin hoga ke main tumhara rab hun? wo kahega , kyon nahin, shetan uskey liye uskey walid aur uskey bhai ki surat ikhtiyar kar lega.'' Asma (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apni kisi zarurat ki khatir tashrif ley gaey, phir wapis aa gaey, aur log aap ke bayan karda farman mein fikr aur gham ki kaifiyat mein they, bayan karti hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne darwazey ki dehleez pakad kar farmaya : ''Asma kya haal hai?'' maine arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! aapney Dajjaal ke zikr se hamarey dil nikal kar rakh diye , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar wo meri zindagi mein nikal aaya to main uska muqabla karunga , warna mera rab her momin par mera khalifa hai.'' maine arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! ham apna aataa goondhti hain aur roti pakka kar abhi farigh bhi nahin hoten ke phir bhook lag jati hai, to us roz mominon ki kya haalat hogi? farmaya : ''tasbih aur taqdees jo aasman walon ke liye kafi hoti hai wohi unke liye kafi hogi.'' rawahu Ahmed."
5492,"Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Dajjaal ke mutalliq , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey, mujh se ziyada kisi ne daryaft nahin kiya, kyonkey aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya : ''wo tumhen nuqsan nahin pahunchaeyga.'' maine arz kiya : wo (log ya yahood aur nasaaraa) kehtey hain ke uskey sath rotiyon ka pahad aur pani ki nehar hogi? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo (Dajjaal) Allah ke nazdik un ashiya (cheezon) ki wajeh se mazeed zaleel hoga.'' muttafaq aleh."
5493,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Dajjaal eik nihayat safed gadhey par Sawar ho kar nikleyga, uskey dono kanon ke beech sattar baa'a (eik baa'a do haathon ki lambaai ke barabar hota hai) fasla hoga.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi al-ba's aur  Nushur) ."
5494,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath mein Sahaba ki eik jamaat ke sath ibne Sayyaad ki taraf rawana huey aur unhoney usey bano Maghaala ke qiley mein bachchon ke sath kheltey huey paya , ibne Sayyaad un dino bulooghat (jawani) ke qarib tha, usey (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki aamad ka ( pata us waqt chala jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uski pusht par haath maara , phir farmaya : ''kya tum gawahi detey ho ke main Allah ka Rasool hun? usney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf (ghusse sey) dekha aur kaha : main gawahi deta hun ke aap anpadhon (arbon) ke Rasool hain, phir ibne Sayyaad ne kaha : kya aap gawahi detey hain ke main Allah ka Rasool hun? Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey zor se dabaayaa aur farmaya : ''main Allah aur uskey Rasulon par eman laya.'' phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ibne Sayyaad se farmaya : ''tum kya dekhtey ho?'' usney kaha : merey paas sachche aur jhoote dono aatey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''terey liye maamla khalat malat (shak mein) kar diya gaya hai.'' Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maine tumharey liye apney dil main eik chiz chupai hai (bataao wo kya hai?) aapney ye baat chupai thi : ''jis din aasman zahir dhooein ke sath aaeyga.'' usney kaha : wo دخ (dhuwan) hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''door ho ja, to apni haisiyat se aage nahin badh sakta.'' umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! kya aap uskey mutalliq mujhey ijazat detey hain ke main usey qatl kar dun? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar to ye wohi (Dajjaal) hai to phir is par ghalba hasil nahin kiya ja sakta, aur agar ye wo nahin to phir uskey qatl karney mein terey liye koi bhalai nahin.'' ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, uskey baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Ubai bin Kab Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ko sath lekar khajoor ke us baagh ki taraf rawana huey jis mein ibne Sayyaad tha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khajoor ke tanon mein chhupney lagey aap chahtey they ke us se pehley ke ibne Sayyaad aap ko dekh ley , aap us se kuchh sun lein , ibne Sayyaad makhmali chadar mein apney bistar par letaa hua tha, aur kuch gunguna raha tha, itney mein ibne Sayyaad ki maa ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekh liya jabkey aap khajoor ke tanon mein chhup rahey they, usney kaha : Saaf ye ibne Sayyaad ka naam hai (dekho !) Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aa gaey, chunanche ibne Sayyaad mutanabbeh (aagah) ho gaya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar wo usko (us haalat par) chhod deti to wo (apney dil ki baat) zahir kar deta.'' Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) logon ko khitab karney ke liye khadey huey aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Allah ki hamd aur sanaa bayan ki jo uski shaan ke laaiq hai. phir Dajjaal ka zikr kiya to farmaya : ''main tumhen us se darata hun, aur her Nabi (Alaihissalam) ne us se apni qom ko daraya hai, Nuh (Alaihissalam) ne bhi apni qom ko daraya lekin main uskey mutalliq tumhen aisi baat bataaunga jo kisi Nabi ne apni qom ko nahin batai, tum khub jaan lo ke wo kaana hai jabkey Allah Taala kaana nahin hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
5495,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) , Abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) Madiney ke kisi raastey mein us (ibne Sayyaad) se miley to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey farmaya : ''kya tum gawahi detey ho ke main Allah ka Rasool hun?'' jawab mein usney kaha ke kya aap gawahi detey ho ke main Allah ka Rasool hun? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main Allah par, uskey farishton par, uski kitabon par aur uskey Rasulon par eman laya.'' to kya dekhta hai? ''usney kaha : main takht ko pani par dekhta hun, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tu shetan ka takht samandar par dekhta hai.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tu (iskey ilawa aur) kya dekhta hai?'' usney kaha : do sachchey aur eik jhoota dekhta hun ya do jhootey aur eik sachcha dekhta hun, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''is par maamla shak mein kar diya gaya hai, tum isey chhod do.'' rawahu Muslim."
5496,Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke ibne Sayyaad ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se jannat ki mitti ke barey mein puchha to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''naram aur mulaaim safed khalis kastoori hai.'' rawahu Muslim.
5497,"Hazrat Naafe bayan kartey hain, ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) Madiney ke kisi raastey mein ibne Sayyaad se miley to unhoney us se koi baat kahi jisney usey naraz kar diya aur ghusse ki wajeh se uski saans phool gaee yahan tak ke raasta bhar gaya (uskey baad) ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu), Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ke paas gaey to unhen us waqie ki ittilaa ho chuki thi, to unhoney unhen farmaya : Allah tum par rehem farmaai , tum ne ibne Sayyaad se kis chiz ka qasd (irada) (jhagda) kiya? kya tumhen ilm nahin ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo (Dajjaal) eik ghussey ki wajeh se niklega jo usey ghussa dilaaya jaeyga.'' rawahu Muslim."
5498,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Makka ki taraf jatey huey ibne Sayyaad ke sath tha, usney mujhey kaha : mujhey logon (ke kalam) se kis qadr takleef pahunchi hai? wo samajhtey hain ke main Dajjaal hun, kya tum ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey nahin suna ke uski aulad nahin hogi.'' jabkey meri aulad hai, kya aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye nahin farmaya ke'' wo kafir hai? ''jabkey main musalman hun, kya aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye nahin farmaya : ''wo Madina mein dakhil hoga na Makka mein.'' jabkey main Madina se aa raha hun aur makkey ja raha hun, phir usney mujh se apni aakhiri baat ye ki : sun lo, Allah ki qism ! main us (Dajjaal) ki jaey paidaish aur waqte-paidaish ko janta hun aur wo kahan hai? ye bhi janta hun, main uskey waliden ko janta hun, Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya, us (ibne Sayyaad) ne mujhey ishtabah (shak) mein dal diya, wo bayan kartey hain, maine usey kaha : terey liye baqi dinon (din) mein tabahi ho, Abu-Saeed bayan kartey hain, usey kaha gaya : kya to ye pasand karta hai ke wo (Dajjaal) tum hi ho? Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, usney kaha : agar wo chiz (Dajjaal ki khaslat aur jibillat waghera) mujh par pesh ki jaey to main napasand nahin karunga. rawahu Muslim."
5499,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main us (ibne Sayyaad) se mila aur uski aankh sooji hui thi, maine kaha : main jo dekh raha hun teri aankh ko kab se aisey hai? usney kaha : main nahin janta , maine kaha : to nahin janta halanke wo terey sar mein hai, usney kaha : agar Allah chahey to wo usey terey asaa mein paida kar dey, ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : wo gadhey se bhi ziyada khofnak aawaz mein cheekhney laga, maine (us ki) aawaz suni. rawahu Muslim."
5500,"Hazrat Muhammad bin Munkadir bayan kartey hain, maine Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ko Allah ki qism uthatey huey suna ke ibne Sayyaad dajjaal hai, maine kaha : aap Allah ki qism uthatey hain, unhoney kaha : maine umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko is baat par Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas qism uthatey huey suna, lekin Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne is par nagawari nahin farmaee. muttafaq aleh."
5501,"Hazrat Naafe bayan kartey hain, ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kiya kartey they, Allah ki qism ! mujhey koi shak nahin ke Masih Dajjaal ibne Sayyaad hi hai. (rawahu Abu-Dawood aur al-Behaqi fi kitab al-ba's aur Nushur)."
5502,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham ne Harra ke din ibne Sayyaad ko na paya. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
5503,"Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Dajjaal ke waliden tees saal tak (be aulad) rahengey aur unke yahan koi bachcha paida nahin hoga, phir unke yahan ladka paida hoga jo kaanaa, badey daanton wala aur bahut hi kam munafaa (faayde) pahunchane-wala hoga, uski aankhen soiegi lekin uska dil nahin soega.'' phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey waliden ke mutalliq hamen Taaruf : karaya, farmaya : '' uska walid lamba, patla hoga aur uski naak lambi hogi, uski walida moti lambey haathon wali hogi.'' Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham ne Madina mein yahudiyon ke yahan eik bachchey ki wiladat ki khabar suni to main aur Zuber bin Awam (Raziallahu anhu) gaey yahan tak ke ham uskey waliden ke paas pahunch gaey, dekha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne jo sifaat bayan ki thin wo un mein mojud thin, ham ne un se kaha : kya tumhara koi bachcha hai? unhoney kaha : ham tees saal tak (be aulad) rahey, aur hamarey yahan koi bachcha paida na hua , phir hamarey yahan eik bachcha paida hua jo kaanaa , lambey daanton wala aur intehai kam nafa-mand hai, uski aankhen soti hain lekin uska dil nahin sota. raawi bayan kartey hain, ham un dono ke paas se nikley to wo eik chadar mein lipta hua dhoop mein zamin par letaa hua tha aur uski aawaz past thi, usney apney sar se kapda uthaya to ye kaha : tum dono ne ye kya kaha tha? ham ne kaha : ham ne jo kaha tha kya to ne usey sun liya tha? usney kaha : haan , meri aankhen soti hain jabkey mera dil nahin sota. rawahu Tirmizi."
5504,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik Yahudi aurat ne Madina main eik bachchey ko janm diya jiski aankh nahin thi, uski kichliya nazar aa rahi thin, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko andesha hua ke wo dajjaal na ho, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey eik chadar ke nichey kuchh ghair wazeh baaten kartey huey paya , uski walida ne usey ittilaa kar di, kaha : Abdullah ! ye to Abu-Qasim (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hain, wo chadar se nikla to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''isey kya hua? Allah isey halak karey, agar wo us (ibne Sayyaad) ko uskey haal par chhod deti to wo (apney dil ki baat) bayan kar deta.'' phir ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees ke maana ki jaisi hadees bayan ki, umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey ijazat marahmat farmaain ke main isey qatl kar dun, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar to ye wohi (Dajjaal) hai to phir tum usey qatl karney waley nahin ho, usey qatl karney waley to Esa bin Maryam (Alaihissalam) hain, aur agar wo (Dajjaal) na hua to phir kisi zimmi shakhs ko qatl karney ka tumhen koi haq hasil nahin.'' Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) musalsal khof-zada rahey ke wo Dajjaal hai. (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah)."
5505,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! albatta qarib hai ke ibn Maryam (Esa (Alaihissalam)) tumharey darmiyan eik aadil haakim ke taur par nazil hongey, wo saleeb tod dengey, khinzir ko maar dalengey, jiziya moquf kar dengey aur maal ki itni rail-pel hogi ke usey leney wala koi nahin milega , yahan tak ke eik sajda duniya aur jo kuchh isme hai, se behtar hoga.'' phir Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey : agar tum chaho to ye aayat padho : ehle-kitab ka her fard un (Esa (Alaihissalam)) ki maut se pehley un par zarur eman ley aaeyga.'' muttafaq aleh."
5506,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ki qism ! ibne Maryam (Esa (Alaihissalam)) hukm aadil (insaf pasand) ki haisiyat se nazil hongey, wo saleeb tod dengey , khinzir ko qatl kar dalengey , jiziya moquf kar dengey , jawan oontniyaan chhod di jaeyngi un se koi kaam nahin liya jaeyga, adawat aur ranjish aur bahami (aapsi) bughz aur hasad jata rahega , wo maal ki taraf bulaeyngey lekin usey koi leney wala nahin hoga.'' rawahu Muslim. aur Saheehain ki riwayat mein hai, farmaya : ''tumhari us waqt kya haalat hogi jab ibne Maryam (Alaihissalam) tumharey darmiyan nuzool farmaeyngey , aur tumhara Imam tum hi mein se hoga.''"
5507,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri ummat ka eik giroh hamesha haq par qitaal karta rahega wo (qurb) qiyame-qiyamat tak ghalib aatey rahengey.'' farmaya : ''ibn Maryam (Alaihissalam) nazil hongey to unka ameer kahega : tashrif laeyn aur hamein Namaz padhaein, wo farmaeyngey , nahin, Allah ne is ummat ko jo izzat bakhshi hai us wajeh se tum khud hi eik doosrey ke Imam ho.'' rawahu Muslim."
5508,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Esa bin Maryam (Alaihissalam) zamin par nazil hongey, shaadi karengey aur unki aulad hogi , wo paintaalees saal rahengey phir faut ho jaeyngey . unhen meri qabr ke sath hi merey qarib dafn kar diya jaeyga. main aur Esa bin Maryam , Abu-Bakar aur umr ke darmiyan se eik hi qabr se khadey hongey.'' ibne Jauzi ne usey kitab al-wafaa mein zikr kiya hai. (rawahu ibn Jauzi fi kitab al-wafaa)."
5509,"Hazrat Shoba Qatada sey, wo Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kartey hain, unhoney kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main aur qiyamat in dono (ungliyon) ki tarah bhejey gaey hain.'' Shoba ne bayan kiya, maine Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se suna wo ye waqia bayan kartey huey kaha kartey they. jis tarah in dono (ungliyon) mein se eik ko dusri par fazilat hasil hai. main nahin janta ke aaya unhoney isey Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se naqal kiya hai ya Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ka apna bayan hai. muttafaq aleh."
5510,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko , unki wafat se eik maah pehley farmatey huey suna : ''tum mujh se qiyamat ke barey mein sawal kartey ho, halanke uska ilm to Allah hi ke paas hai, main Allah ki qism uthata hun ke roey zamin par jo zi-rooh aaj mojud hai wo so saal guzarney ke baad zinda nahin hogi.'' rawahu Muslim."
5511,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu), Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''roey zamin par jo nafs aaj mojud hai, so saal guzarney ke baad wo zinda nahin hoga.'' rawahu Muslim."
5512,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, kuchh Erabi (dehati) (dehati) log Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur unhoney aap se qiyamat ke mutalliq sawal kiya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un mein se sab se chhotey ki taraf dekhtey huey farmaya : ''agar ye zinda raha to iskey boodhey honey se pehley tumhari qiyamat tum par qaaim ho jaeygi.'' muttafaq aleh."
5513,"Hazrat Mastur bin Shaddad (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey qiyamat ke zuhoor ke sath bheja gaya hai, main is par isi tarah sabqat ley gaya hun jis tarah ye is par sabqat ley gaee hai.'' aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apni do ungliyon, angusht shahadat aur darmiyani ungli ke sath ishara kiya. rawahu Tirmizi."
5514,"Hazrat Saad bin Abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main ummid karta hun ke meri ummat apney rab ke yahan aajiz nahin aaeygi ke wo unhen aadha din muakhkhar (der) kar dey.'' Saad (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha gaya, aadhey din ki kya miqdaar hai? unhoney farmaya : paanch-sau-saal. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
5515,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''is duniya ki misal is kapdey ki tarah hai jisey uskey awwal se aakhir tak phaad diya gaya ho aur wo apney aakhir main eik dhaagey ke sath mutalliq ho, qarib hai ke wo dhaaga bhi toot jaey.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
5516,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tak zamin par Allah Allah kaha jaeyga qiyamat qaaim nahin hogi.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''kisi eik par qiyamat qaaim nahin hogi jab tak wo Allah Allah kehta ho.'' rawahu Muslim.
5517,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qiyamat bad-tareen logon par qaaim hogi.'' rawahu Muslim."
5518,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qiyamat qaaim nahin hogi yahan tak ke qabila dos ki aurton ke peeth zul-khalasa ke gird (tawaf kartey huey) chhalken (yani harkat keren) gi. aur zul-khalasa dos qabiley ka sanam hai jiski wo daure-jahiliyat mein puja kiya kartey they. muttafaq aleh."
5519,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''raat aur din khatam nahin hongey yahan tak ke Laat aur Uzza ki puja ki jaeygi.'' maine arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! jab Allah ne ye aayat nazil farmaee : ''wo zaat jisney apney Rasool ko hidayat aur Deen haq de-kar Nabi banakar bheja ta ke wo usey tamam deeno par ghalib kar dey chahey (chaahe) mushrik usey nagawar janen.'' to main khayal karti thi ke ye (hukm tamam zamanon ko) shamil hoga? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''is (deen ke mukammal karney) mein jo Allah chaheyga wohi ho jaeyga, phir Allah eik khushgawar hawa chalaeyga us waqt jis shakhs ke dil mein raai ke daney ke barabar eman hoga wo wafat pa jaeyga, aur sirf wohi baqi reh jaeyngey jin mein koi khair nahin hogi , wo apney baap-daada ke Deen ki taraf lot jaeyngey.'' rawahu Muslim."
5520,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Dajjaal nikleyga to wo chaalis qiyam kerega.'' (Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain) main nahin janta ke chaalis din ya chaalis maah ya chaalis saal '' phir Allah Eisaa bin Maryam (Alaihissalam) ko bhejeyga goya wo Urwa bin Masood hain, wo us (Dajjaal) ko talash karengey aur usey qatl karengey , phir wo logon ke darmiyan saat saal rahengey , kisi do ke darmiyan koi adawat nahin hogi , phir Allah Sham ki taraf se thandi hawa bhejeyga to wo roey zamin par mojud un tamam logon ki rooh qabz kar leygi jinkey dil mein raai ke daney ke barabar eman ya khair hogi , yahan tak ke agar tum mein se koi pahad ke andar ghus jaeyga to wo wahan pahunch kar usey daboch leygi.'' farmaya : ''bad-tareen log baqi reh jaeyngey jo parindon ki tarah subuk aur tez jabkey darindon ki tarah sakht (wehshi) hongey, wo kisi neki ko neki samjhengey na burai ko burai , shetan roop badal kar unko kahega : kya tum haya nahin kartey? wo kahengey : tum hamen kya hukm detey ho? chunanche wo unhen buton ki puja karney ki talqin kerega, aur wo usi haalat mein hongey, unka rizq bahut ziyada hoga, unki zindagi khushgawar hogi , phir Soor phunk diya jaeyga, jo shakhs usey suney ga wo apni gardan ko eik janib jhukaeyga aur eik janib uthaeyga.'' farmaya : ''sab se pehley usey wo shakhs suneyga jo apney oonton ke hoz ki lipaai kar raha hoga, wo be-hosh ho jaeyga aur tamam log be-hosh ho jaeyngey, phir Allah shabnam ki tarah barish barsaeyga jis se logon ke jism ug (ji) padengey, phir dusri martaba Soor phunka jaeyga to wo achcha khadey ho kar dekhney lagengey, phir kaha jaeyga : logo ! apney rab ki taraf aao, (farishton se kaha jaeyga) unhen khada karo kyonkey un se hisab liya jaeyga, phir (farishton se kaha jaeyga) aag walon (jahannamiyon) ko nikal laao (alag kar do). kaha jaeyga : kitney mein se kitney? kaha jaeyga : hazar mein se nau-sau-ninnanwey.'' farmaya : ''ye wo din hai jo bacchhon ko boodha kar dega, aur ye wo din hai jis din pindli se kapda hata diya jaeyga.'' rawahu Muslim. aur Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees : ''hijrat munqata' nahin hogi'' (باب التوب) mein zikr ki gaee hai."
